vWashington House Rabbit Newsv

Volume 7  Issue 1 March 1998


Dr. Cindy Bishop is on the Move

We love our bunnies! Therefore, it is of great importance and peace of mind to have an excellent veterinarian we can trust to keep our bunnies healthy. One such veterinarian that is a big favorite of HRS, is Dr. Cindy Bishop. Dr. Bishop is relocating her practice to two local veterinary hospitals. Her services will be divided between All Care Pet Hospital in Mukilteo, and All Pet Veterinary Clinic in North Seattle (yes, with Dr. Deeb, another HRS favorite!).

Dr. Bishop is one (of only a few) of HRS' highly recommended veterinarians in rabbit health care in Western Washington. HRS seeks her advice and services frequently and with great confidence. Dr. Bishop's truly genuine compassion for animals and exceptional knowledge in rabbit health care is no secret, just ask us at HRS.
